{"product_id":"madara-clarifying-toner-200ml","title":"MÁDARA Clarifying Toner 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDeeply exfoliate clogged and oily skin with this clarifying toner. Formulated with oil-controlling extracts of oak bark and sweet flag (root), floral water and natural moisturisers it purifies the skin, reduces shine, minimises pores, prevents blemishes and regulates the skin’s natural pH balance. Leaves the skin looking fresh, clean and matte. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003ePackaged in a 100% post-consumer recycled bottle.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply in the morning and night to clean skin with a cotton pad or splash on with hands. Follow with moisturiser.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e AQUA; ALCOHOL; ROSA DAMASCENA (ROSE) FLOWER WATER*; GLYCERIN**; ACORUS CALAMUS (SWEET FLAG) ROOT EXTRACT*; CUCUMIS SATIVUS (CUCUMBER) FRUIT EXTRACT*; BETAINE; QUERCUS ROBUR (OAK) BARK EXTRACT*; SALVIA OFFICINALIS (SALVIA) LEAF EXTRACT*; SALICYLIC ACID; BENZYL ALCOHOL; SODIUM BENZOATE; POTASSIUM SORBATE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e35% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53351797686599,"sku":null,"price":17.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-clarifying-toner-200ml-8014361.jpg?v=1771463662","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-clarifying-toner-200ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}